<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Organizer Dashboard - South African Sports Association</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@100;200;300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <style>
        .dashboard-container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 30px;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .dashboard-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        
        .dashboard-title {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .dashboard-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .dashboard-btn {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #f44336;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .dashboard-btn:hover {
            background: #e41c0c;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        
        .dashboard-content {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 30px;
        }
        
        .dashboard-card {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .dashboard-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .dashboard-card h3 {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .dashboard-card p {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .card-footer {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .card-stat {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
        }
        
        .card-action {
            color: #f44336;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .event-list {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        
        .event-list h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .event-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        
        .event-table th {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd;
        }
        
        .event-table td {
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        
        .event-table tr:hover {
            background: #f9f9f9;
        }
        
        .status {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .status.active {
            background: #e6f7e6;
            color: #28a745;
        }
        
        .status.pending {
            background: #fff3cd;
            color: #ffc107;
        }
        
        .status.completed {
            background: #e2e3e5;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        
        .action-btn {
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #fff;
            background: #f44336;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .action-btn:hover {
            background: #e41c0c;
        }
        
        @media(max-width: 992px) {
            .dashboard-content {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
        }
        
        @media(max-width: 768px) {
            .dashboard-content {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .dashboard-header {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            
            .dashboard-actions {
                width: 100%;
            }
            
            .dashboard-btn {
                flex: 1;
                text-align: center;
            }
            
            .event-table {
                display: block;
                overflow-x: auto;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <section class="sub-header">
        <nav>
            <a href="/"><img src="/images/sports-amigo-logo.png" alt="South African Sports Association Logo"></a>
            <div class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
                <i class="fa fa-times" onclick="hideMenu()"></i>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/">HOME</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/about">ABOUT</a></li>
                    <li class="dropdown">
                        <a href="/events">EVENTS</a>
                        <div class="dropdown-content">
                            <a href="/events/football">Football</a>
                            <a href="/events/cricket">Cricket</a>
                            <a href="/events/basketball">Basketball</a>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li><a href="/contact">CONTACT</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/partner">PARTNER</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/support">SUPPORT</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/logout">LOGOUT</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <i class="fa fa-bars" onclick="showMenu()"></i>
        </nav>
        <h1>Organizer Dashboard</h1>
    </section>

    <div class="dashboard-container">
        <div class="dashboard-header">
            <h2 class="dashboard-title">Welcome, Organizer!</h2>
            <div class="dashboard-actions">
                <button class="dashboard-btn">Create Event</button>
                <button class="dashboard-btn">Manage Venues</button>
                <button class="dashboard-btn">Reports</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="dashboard-content">
            <div class="dashboard-card">
                <h3>Active Events</h3>
                <p>You have 3 active events currently running.</p>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <span class="card-stat">Total participants: 245</span>
                    <a href="#" class="card-action">View Events</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="dashboard-card">
                <h3>Upcoming Events</h3>
                <p>You have 5 events scheduled in the next 30 days.</p>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <span class="card-stat">Next event: Tomorrow</span>
                    <a href="#" class="card-action">Manage Schedule</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="dashboard-card">
                <h3>Registration Stats</h3>
                <p>Your events have 120 new registrations this week.</p>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <span class="card-stat">Conversion rate: 68%</span>
                    <a href="#" class="card-action">View Analytics</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="dashboard-card">
                <h3>Revenue</h3>
                <p>Your events have generated R25,000 in revenue this month.</p>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <span class="card-stat">+15% from last month</span>
                    <a href="#" class="card-action">Financial Reports</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="dashboard-card">
                <h3>Venue Management</h3>
                <p>You have 4 venues booked for upcoming events.</p>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <span class="card-stat">Next booking: Cape Town Stadium</span>
                    <a href="#" class="card-action">Manage Venues</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="dashboard-card">
                <h3>Support Tickets</h3>
                <p>You have 5 open support tickets from event participants.</p>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <span class="card-stat">Oldest ticket: 2 days</span>
                    <a href="#" class="card-action">View Tickets</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="event-list">
            <h2>Recent Events</h2>
            <table class="event-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Event Name</th>
                        <th>Date</th>
                        <th>Location</th>
                        <th>Participants</th>
                        <th>Status</th>
                        <th>Actions</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Cape Town Marathon</td>
                        <td>15 May 2023</td>
                        <td>Cape Town Stadium</td>
                        <td>120</td>
                        <td><span class="status active">Active</span></td>
                        <td>
                            <button class="action-btn">Manage</button>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Johannesburg Football Cup</td>
                        <td>22 May 2023</td>
                        <td>Ellis Park Stadium</td>
                        <td>85</td>
                        <td><span class="status active">Active</span></td>
                        <td>
                            <button class="action-btn">Manage</button>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Durban Cricket Tournament</td>
                        <td>30 May 2023</td>
                        <td>Kingsmead Cricket Ground</td>
                        <td>40</td>
                        <td><span class="status pending">Pending</span></td>
                        <td>
                            <button class="action-btn">Manage</button>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Pretoria Basketball Championship</td>
                        <td>10 April 2023</td>
                        <td>Pretoria Indoor Arena</td>
                        <td>65</td>
                        <td><span class="status completed">Completed</span></td>
                        <td>
                            <button class="action-btn">View Report</button>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Bloemfontein Athletics Meet</td>
                        <td>5 April 2023</td>
                        <td>Free State Stadium</td>
                        <td>95</td>
                        <td><span class="status completed">Completed</span></td>
                        <td>
                            <button class="action-btn">View Report</button>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="footer">
        <h4>About South African Sports Association</h4>
        <p>The South African Sports Association is dedicated to promoting sports and physical activity across South Africa.<br>We provide opportunities for athletes of all ages and abilities to participate in a variety of sports.</p>
        <div class="icons">
            <a href="#"><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i></a>
            <a href="#"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></a>
            <a href="#"><i class="fa fa-instagram"></i></a>
            <a href="#"><i class="fa fa-linkedin"></i></a>
        </div>
        <p>Made with <i class="fa fa-heart-o"></i> by South African Sports Association</p>
    </section>

    <script>
        var navLinks = document.getElementById("navLinks");
        
        function showMenu() {
            navLinks.style.right = "0";
        }
        
        function hideMenu() {
            navLinks.style.right = "-200px";
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html> 